http://www.examiner.com/article/officials-li-woman-exhibiting-flu-like-symptoms-does-not-have-ebola
[Suspected Ebola case of a woman experiencing flu-like symptoms who 1st stated she had recently been to Africa. HazMat crews were called to her neighborhood. It was later found she had not been in areas experiencing an Ebola outbreak. State and county health officials determined she did not have Ebola]

